  "readingTitle": "Misconception check",
  "reading": "<p><strong>❌ Common misconception:</strong> ‘La red social’ means ‘a red social event’.</p><p><strong>✅ The correct idea:</strong> ‘La red social’ means ‘a social network’.</p>",
